metadata.description: 10000 NFT Collection 200 unique traits An exclusive ticket into the BATC metaverse. We know, the world out there is getting pretty crazy and staying indoors is driving everyone BORED,  ApeTeens especially. The typical Bored Ape Teen is one who is no longer satisfied to be defined and treated as a Little Ape Kid anymore;  the BoredApeTeen wants FREEDOM and INDEPENDENCE! But how does the BoredApeTeen navigate the NFT universe that offers so much, yet tells so little? Enter the Bored Ape Teen Club!  As part of our vision for our community, BATC NFTs will bridge the gap between the NFT space and the physical world. As our community grows and its reach extends, we will embark on collaborations with other like-minded Apes to brave new frontiers. You ask where can your BoredApeTeen bring you? We say the BoredApeTeen can go anywhere it dreams of.
metadata.name: Bored Ape Teen Club #1
